---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'July 19, 2026';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service | Barbara Kohler Seminars" description="The terms that govern use of barbarakohlerseminars.com and enrollment in our classes.">
  <main id="top">
    <section class="legal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow on-light">Legal</span>
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

        <p>These terms govern your use of <strong>barbarakohlerseminars.com</strong> and enrollment in classes offered by Barbara Kohler Seminars, PLLC (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;). By using the site or enrolling, you agree to these terms.</p>

        <h2>Classes & enrollment</h2>
        <p>When you enroll and complete payment, you receive access to the class and its materials for your personal, non-commercial use. Course content, workbooks, and downloads are our intellectual property and may not be copied, resold, or redistributed.</p>

        <h2>Payment</h2>
        <p>Class fees are shown at checkout and processed securely by Stripe. Enrollment is confirmed once payment is received.</p>

        <h2>Refunds</h2>
        <p>Our refund terms are described in our <a href="/refund-policy">Refund Policy</a>.</p>

        <h2>Nature of our teaching</h2>
        <p>Our classes offer faith-based personal-growth teaching from a Biblical worldview. They are educational and ministry in nature and are <strong>not</strong> a substitute for professional medical, psychological, legal, or financial advice. For licensed clinical counseling, see <a href="https://www.thekohlergroup.net">The Kohler Group</a>.</p>

        <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to misuse the site, attempt to disrupt it, or use it in violation of applicable law.</p>

        <h2>Disclaimer & limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>The site and classes are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranties of any kind. To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any indirect or consequential damages arising from your use of the site or classes.</p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms from time to time; the &ldquo;last updated&rdquo; date reflects the latest version.</p>

        <h2>Governing law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of North Carolina, without regard to conflict-of-law rules.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:barbara@barbarakohlerseminars.com">barbara@barbarakohlerseminars.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  .legal{padding:64px 0 88px;background:#fff}
  .legal .wrap{max-width:760px}
  .legal h1{font-size:34px;color:var(--navy-ink);margin:8px 0 6px}
  .legal h2{font-size:20px;color:var(--navy-ink);margin:30px 0 10px}
  .legal p,.legal li{line-height:1.7;color:#2a2a2a}
  .updated{color:#6a7686;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
  .legal a{color:var(--sapphire);font-weight:600}
</style>
